quran[16]{c,v,t}:
  19,83,“Kodi suona kuti Ife timawatuma asatana kwa osakhulupirira ndipo akuwakhwirizira kwambiri (kuchita zoipa)
  19,84,"“Choncho, usawachitire changu (kuti alangidwe tsopano), ndithu Ife tikuwawerengera chiwerengero (cha masiku awo; masiku akakwana, tiwalanga)"
  19,85,“(Kumbukira iwe Mtumiki) tsiku lomwe tidzawasonkhanitsa oopa (Allah) kunka nawo kwa Mwini chifundo Chambiri ali m’magulumagulu monga nthumwi (Zake kuti apatsidwe ulemu)
  19,86,“Ndipo oipa tidzawakusa kunka nawo ku Moto ali ndi ludzu lalikulu monga momwe ziweto zimathamangira kupita kumadzi zikakhala ndi ludzu lalikulu
  19,87,“Sadzakhala ndi mphamvu yoombolera (ena) koma kupatula omwe adagwiritsa lonjezo la (Allah) Mwini chifundo chambiri
  19,88,"“Ndipo (osakhulupirira omwe ndi Ayuda ndi Akhirisitu) akuti: “(Allah) Mwini chifundo chambiri wadzipangira mwana!”"
  19,89,“Ndithu mwadza ndi chinthu choipitsitsa (pazimene mukunenazi)
  19,90,"“Thambo layandikira kusweka ndi mawuwo, ndipo nthaka kuphwasuka, ndipo mapiri kugwa ndikudukaduka"
  19,91,“Chifukwa chakumunamizira (Allah) Mwini chifundo chambiri kuti ali ndi mwana
  19,92,“Ndipo nkosayenera kwa (Allah) Mwini Chifundo chambiri kudzipangira mwana
  19,93,“Palibe aliyense yemwe ali kumwamba ndi pansi koma adzadza kwa (Allah) Mwini Chifundo chambiri ali kapolo (Wake)
  19,94,“Ndithu (Allah) wawadziwa mokwanira ndipo adzawawerenga aliyense payekhapayekha
  19,95,"“Ndipo, aliyense wa iwo adzadza kwa Iye (Allah) ali payekhapayekha"
  19,96,"“Ndithu amene akhulupirira ndikumachita zabwino, (Allah) Mwini chifundo chambiri adzaika chikondi pakati pawo"
  19,97,“Ndithu taifewetsa (Qur’an) m’chiyankhulo chako kuti ndi iyo uwawuze nkhani zabwino oopa Allah ndipo ndi iyo uwachenjeze anthu amakani
  19,98,"“Kodi ndi mibadwo ingati tidaiononga patsogolo pawo? Kodi ukumuona mmodzi wa iwo, kapena ukumva mgugu wawo"